name: VIVO Advisor Training Course - WEBinar
description:
VIVO Advisors are trained facilitators that embody the principal’s of both GAGU, Gathering a Greater Understanding The Ultimate Life Guide for Youth and Who Am I? for Preteens & Teens. Trained by Master Mentor, Cora Dunham, VIVO Advisors are competent speakers who share the teaching strategies of author, Cora Coleman-Dunham, and have a unique passion for the empowerment and well-being of youth and young adults. VIVO Advisors exemplify integrity and understand the value of mentoring and appropriate, yet transparent communication with youth regardless of their socio-economic background. 

The goal is equip the mentees with tools that will help them recognize and develop their self-worth, goal setting and practical application for life skills and career strategies in order to maximize their full potential from the inside – out. 

Income earning potential for VIVO Advisors is limitless

name: Who Am I? for Preteens by Cora Dunham [English]
description: Who Am I? is an excellent book for young girls and boys as they develop mentally, emotionally and physically into beautiful and confident young people. It walks them through their internal journey of understanding and developing self-esteem, recognizing positive and negative influences, conflict resolution and The 6 Essential Identity Links. Who Am I? is a MUST-HAVE preteen book to prepare for life from the inside - out!

name: ¿Quién Soy Yo? por Cora Dunham [Español]
description:
¿Quién Soy Yo? es un excelente libro para los jóvenes, a medida que se van desarrollando mental, emocional, y físicamente para ser jóvenes adultos hermosos y seguros de si mismo. Les ayuda caminar en su viaje interno de comprensión y desarrollo de auto-estima, reconociendo las influencias positivas y negativas, resolviendo conflictos, y conociendo los 6 Enlaces Esenciales de Identidad.

¿Quién Soy Yo? es un libro NECESARIO que cada joven debe tener para prepararse en la vida ¡desde adentro hacia afuera!

name: Creating a Culture of Connectivity, Manual for Ministry by Carl Davis, Edited by Cora Dunham
description: Creating a Culture of Connectivity serves as an invaluable manual for all ministries. As the Senior Pastor of The New Life Tabernacle Church in Houston, Texas, Carl Davis has relied on the power and leading of the Holy Spirit with both a Christian and Corporate background to develop this ultimate resource guide which provides detailed layout for effective ministry.

name: Reinvigorate Album-Josh Dunham
description:
Josh Dunham, renowned bassist for pop artist Prince, is set to release his highly anticipated first album Reinvigorate!!

Reinvigorate is a compilation of genres that infuses the soul with energy and strength to aspire for greatness in all walks of life. The definition of reinvigorate is literally ‘to give new energy or strength to’ and this album does just that. The album includes contributions from such talents as Terrence Vaughn, (producer/pianist) Rhonda Smith( former bassist for Prince); Jerry Henry (pianist), Tim Stewart, (guitarist for American Idol Tour) Nakitta Clegg-Foxx, (vocalist with Kurt Carr Singers), Donald Hayes (saxophonist/film scorer), LeJuan Samual  (producer/vocalist) Terry Banks (drummer/producer) and Cora Dunham (writer/percussionist).

name: Shawni Richardson's Sounds of the Season
description:
If you are looking for the perfect blend of seasonal melodies, look no further. Baltimore native, Shawni Richardson is a class act and gives a peak into her versatility as a vocalist. Sounds of the Season includes Will You Have Room both in full score and an instrumental version. She also displays her cultural diversity with an awesome bilingual rendition of O Come All Ye Faithful featuring Daisy Garcia!

This is a must have prelude to Shawni's full album that will be released this year! For more info on Shawni Richardson visit:

www.shawnirichardson.com

name: G.A.G.U. Gathering A Greater Understanding, The Ultimate Life Guide for  Youth
description:
[Available in English & Spanish]
The book, entitled G.A.G.U, Gathering A Greater Understanding is a is an interactive workbook that serves as the ultimate life guide for all young people. What makes G.A.G.U. unique is that it explains in detail, ALL of a young person’s options after high school and encourages the habit of learning for the sake of overall growth in order to be best equipped for adulthood. 

Not only does G.A.G.U. make clear the options of College, Trade School, The Work Force, and the Military, it addresses real responsibilities that school does not always prepare you for…LIFE-establishing credit, buying a car, getting a passport, understanding finances and more!! Whether you are approaching 9th grade, a high school graduate undecided about life or you are a concerned teacher or parent looking for direction, there is no book that offers a young person a view of every aspect after high school until now!

name: Kick Snare Hat 2 DISC HD-DVD
description:
Kick Snare Hat Drums DVD - The Superstar Drummers of Hip Hop and R&B DVD featuring Cora Coleman-Dunham and her friends, Gerald Heyward, Nissan Stewart and Aaron Spears - The heartbeat of hip-hop and R&B comes from the streets. It ís a dream that never dies and a lifestyle that only a few drummers will get to live. From the inner cities to the churches, and from the woodsheds to the arena stages, the drummers that play this music all have a story to tell and it is as real as it gets. 

Join  Cora Colman-Dunham and her friends Gerald Heyward, Nissan Stewart, Aaron Spears as they take you on the ride of a lifetime. Learn what inspires them, drives then, and takes them to the top of their game. Shot in HD, this two-DVD set includes tons of behind the scenes footage, interviews, playing footage, and bonus features with the genre's elite. And for the first time ever on film, they are playing together in one room. If you love music you'll love Kick Snare Hat.

Running Time approx. 61 mins (total content 116 mins).

name: PRIVATE Bass LESSONS - King Josh (45 minutes)
description:
Study with a pro!
Houston native, King Josh Dunham, is internationally recognized for his 5-year performance performance experience with Prince as well as, singer/songwriter, Frank McComb, Lalah Hathaway, Vanessa Bell Armstrong, Kurt Carr, Patti Labelle and others. His solid, FUNKY yet tasteful expression as a bassist was heard everywhere from Italy, Germany and 21 Nights in London (O2 Arena) to the Montreaux Jazz Festival, 3121 in Las Vegas and the infamous Superbowl XLI Halftime Show! 

His television appearances are vast and recently released his own solo recording project, REINVIGORATE. He is also the owner of the custom bass guitar company Dunham Custom Designs.

He is currently the bassist with Nick Jonas.

name: "Queen Cora" Cora Coleman-Dunham Signature Stick
description:
Length: 16-1/2"
Diameter: 0.53"

Vater Cora Coleman-Dunham Model Drumsticks
The design of these Vater drumsticks is as versatile as Cora Coleman-Dunham herself. Performing with Prince, Cora needed a drumstick that could cover all genres of music without changing models. Cora’s design combines a little extra length and a gradual taper to an acorn tip to offer superb response, feel and dynamics in any musical application.

Acorn tips produce a full, fat sound. Very responsive.
